dooyit.parser

Interface ParserCommons

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddCategoryParser, AddParser, DeleteCategoryParser, DeleteParser, EditCategoryParser, EditParser, FloatParser, MarkParser, MoveParser, SearchParser, TagParser, UnmarkParser, UnmoveParser

    public interface ParserCommons
    ParserCommons interface contains all the constants and methods that are shared by two or more parser classes.

    Annabel
